 the modern sources, sinks, concentrations and lifetimes of these gases\nand summaries the literature on Archean sources and concentrations. We\nrecommend the forcings provided here be used both as a first reference for\nwhich gases are likely good greenhouse gases, and as a standard set of\ncalculations for validation of radiative forcing calculations for the Archean.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 5 Sep 2014 17:32:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-09-08"}
